年的農業歷史。<ref name="time201704">{{cite news |url=http://time.com/doomsday-vault/ |title=Inside the 'Doomsday' Vault |work=Time |first=Jennifer |last=Duggan |date=2017-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408091443/http://time.com/doomsday-vault/ |archive-date=2017-04-08 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>

