== 保存情况 ==
[[File:Storage_containers_in_Svalbard_Global_Seed_Vault_01.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Aluminium_bags_for_seed_storage_at_Svalbard.jpg|thumb]]
種子庫將種子[[真空|真空]]密封在三層鋁箔包裝中，<ref name="Woodward"/>再將其放入[[塑膠|塑膠]]容器內並置於儲存庫的金屬架上，<ref name="Crop Trust3"/>種子儲存庫的溫度長期由製冷機維持在[[攝氏|攝氏]]-18℃，並同時降低庫內的[[氧氣|氧氣]]量，因低溫和缺氧可降低種子的[[代謝運動|代謝活動]]進而延緩其老化。<ref name="regjeringen-faq">{{cite web |url=http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/lmd/campain/svalbard-global-seed-vault/frequently-asked-questions.html |title=Svalbard Global Seed Vault: Frequently Asked Questions |publisher=農業和食品部 |accessdate=2011-07-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111021223103/http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/lmd/campain/svalbard-global-seed-vault/frequently-asked-questions.html |archivedate=2011-10-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>即使電力中斷使製冷機停止運轉，種子庫周圍的永久凍土也可協助保持其溫度在-8℃左右。<ref name="Joseph Netto"/><ref name="regjeringen-mo">{{cite web |url=http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/lmd/campain/svalbard-global-seed-vault/management-and-operations.html |title=Svalbard Global Seed Vault: Management and Operations |publisher=農業和食品部 |accessdate=2011-07-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327175030/http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/lmd/campain/svalbard-global-seed-vault/management-and-operations.html |archivedate=2010-03-27 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

自種子庫完工以來，每年春季的融雪期間種子庫的入口會有少量的雪水流入，但在2016年10月因異常高溫和暴雨，導致大量的水入侵種子庫入口，最終在進入隧道約15公尺處結凍，並未影響儲存庫中的種子。<ref name="Joseph Netto">{{Cite web|title=Water breaches 'Doomsday' vault entrance, seeds unharmed|url=https://www.cnn.com/2017/05/21/us/doomsday-seed-vault-water-breach/index.html|date=2017-05-22|accessdate=2020-02-02|author1=Joseph Netto|author2=Darran Simon|work=CNN|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202083121/https://www.cnn.com/2017/05/21/us/doomsday-seed-vault-water-breach/index.html|archive-date=2020-02-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年完工的工程解決了庫中的滲水問題。<ref>{{Cite web |title=SVALBARD GLOBALE FRØKVELV |url=https://www.statsbygg.no/prosjekter-og-eiendommer/svalbard-globale-frohvelv |access-date=2022-03-22 |publisher=Statsbygg |language=no |archive-date=2021-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624201823/https://www.statsbygg.no/prosjekter-og-eiendommer/svalbard-globale-frohvelv |dead-url=no }}</ref>

附於種子箱上的膠片為一種[[奈米|奈米]]薄膜，可儲存種子基本資訊和其他訊息。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-02-14 |title=Nanofilm will safeguard identity of the more than 1 mill seed samples in the Seed Vault |url=https://www.seedvault.no/news/nanofilm-will-safeguard-identity-of-the-more-than-1-mill-seed-samples-in-the-seed-vault/ |access-date=2022-03-04 |website=Svalbard Global Seed Vault |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304114947/https://www.seedvault.no/news/nanofilm-will-safeguard-identity-of-the-more-than-1-mill-seed-samples-in-the-seed-vault/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

