== 影視文化 ==
斯瓦爾巴全球種子庫是易卜生國際（Ibsen International）藝術項目《種子》（''The Seed''）的靈感來源，該項目並得到挪威政府的支持。其中由挪威作曲家[[馬庫斯·鮑斯|馬庫斯·鮑斯]]創作的兒童歌劇《{{tsl|en|Children of Ginko|銀杏之子}}》（{{lang|no|''Frøbarna''}}）旨在提升生態意識，並「揭示大自然的力量和讚揚孩子成長的勇氣」。<ref name="Ibsen">{{cite web |url=https://ibseninternational.com/productions/children-of-ginko-premiere-in-shanghai/ |title=Children of Ginko – Premiere in Shanghai |publisher=Ibsen International |access-date=2020-12-23 |language=en |archive-date=2021-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210630023402/https://ibseninternational.com/productions/children-of-ginko-premiere-in-shanghai/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.klassiskmusikk.com/nyheter/marcus-paus-premiere-i-shanghai/ |title=Marcus Paus-premiere i Shanghai |date=2020-11-06 |website=Klassisk musikk |access-date=2020-12-23 |language=no |archive-date=2021-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218022935/https://www.klassiskmusikk.com/nyheter/marcus-paus-premiere-i-shanghai/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

種子庫也曾於2011年11月21日播出的美國喜劇動畫《[[飛出個未來|飛出個未來]]》假日特別節目「{{tsl|en|The Futurama Holiday Spectacular|飛出個未來假日盛典}}」中出現。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Futurama Holiday Spectacular - The Infosphere, the Futurama Wiki|url=https://theinfosphere.org/The_Futurama_Holiday_Spectacular|access-date=2021-06-20|website=The Infosphere|language=en|archive-date=2021-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210914025859/http://theinfosphere.org/The_Futurama_Holiday_Spectacular|dead-url=no}}</ref>

